## Verb dataset and generated learning content

The verb dataset under `src/data/verbs/` includes frequency metadata, lexical information, translations, examples, and derived/enriched material. To keep redistribution compatible with Wiktionary-derived material, the dataset and generated learning content are made available under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-SA 4.0), except where a source imposes different or additional terms.

